      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Leonard H. Stringfield, Advertising Manager,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "DuBois Chemical Company, Inc., 7th and Broadway,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Cincinnati, Ohio, residence, 4412 Grove Avenue,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Mariemont, Cincinnati, Ohio, advised on September 25,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "1961, that he is active in unidentified flying objects",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "research, that he has published a bulletin concerning",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "these matters, that he is well known in this field,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "and that he has worked with the Air Defense Command",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "concerning matters relating to unidentified flying",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "objects.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Mr. Stringfield advised that he recently",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "appeared on a television program known as Impact News",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "on television station WCPO-TV, Cincinnati, Ohio,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "appearing on Sunday, September 10, 1961, at which",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "time he was questioned by a panel of three members",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "concerning matters relating to unidentified flying",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "objects.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Mr. Stringfield advised that at approximately",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "9:00 A.M. on September 25, 1961, he had received an",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "anonymous telephone call, being male caller, whose",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "voice he described as firm, clear, and who spoke good",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "English. The caller related that he had very important",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "information to relate to Mr. Stringfield, whom he",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "asked for by name in his call, relating to unidentified",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "flying objects. Mr. Stringfield related that the caller",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "THIS IS LOANED TO YOU BY THE FBI,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "AND NEITHER IT NOR ITS CONTENTS",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "ARE TO BE DISTRIBUTED OUTSIDE THE",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "AGENCY TO WHICH LOANED.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
